{"tid":1685934,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果你怕網絡禁制令","createTime":"2019-11-01T00:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T00:39:46.000Z","uid":190295,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06642bdb721c7ba9d4a567ffebad907b451885ec","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:26:13.000Z","msg":"轉FB 雁橋曰 -- 數據旅人的日常生活<br />\n原文： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/979668872066287/posts/2792107187489104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F979668872066287%2Fposts%2F2792107187489104%2F&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=a62dc71b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/979668872066287/posts/2792107187489104/</a><br />\n<br />\n【語言很有趣】淺談白癡的禁制令<br />\n<br />\n以事論事，提出禁制令的人不是沒腦袋，就是沒讀過書。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個研究語言的 DS ，就跟大家討論一下禁制令含糊之處。<br />\n<br />\n 語言的一個美妙之處，除了可以交換文字中的 Context 之外，「語境」也是相當重要，所以沒有記憶力的人是無法進行溝通，那麼我們看看禁制令是如何寫：<br />\n<br />\n//律政司申請頒發臨時禁制令，禁止任何人在網上及其他平台，包括但不限於連登及Telegram，發布言論去鼓勵、協助、煽動或教唆其他人使用或威脅用暴力去傷人或損毀財物//<br />\n<br />\n很好，那麼如何定義「鼓勵、協助、煽動或教唆其他人使用或威脅用暴力去傷人或損毀財物」呢？<br />\n<br />\n舉個簡單例子：<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄講：「大家唔好去裝修美心、元氣呀，人地冇生意好慘架。」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又講：「大家唔好去裝修美心、元氣呀，人地冇生意好慘架。」<br />\n<br />\n我地會知道兩句說話隱含的意思都有不同，那麼你可以說梁國雄犯法，然而梁振英沒有嗎？如果這個情況成立，網上只要把「鼓吹」的方式改變為「千其唔好做」就解決了，你難以去入罪。<br />\n<br />\n又或者係我咁和理非叫人罷買罷食：「美心係藍店，千其唔好幫襯」，你會唔會當我係協助或教唆人去破壞美心？語言文字的 Context 有時不流於表面，而是需要接收者進一步理解，這也是為什麼 A.I. 仍然未能完全理解人類語言的原因。<br />\n<br />\n如果政府仍然打算制造白色恐怖和文字獄，就實在太天真了，亦永遠不會成功。<br />\n<br />\n昨日我在太子站外面望了一陣，不絕的人群，代表我們不會忘記，以後也不會放低。<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命"},{"pid":"9c876edeab4e603f3c97fc38af3b383a223401f5","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"1/10 曱近平"},{"pid":"4ac1890bda31d123564c92b0285fcc934ed84ff2","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"2/10 曱甴平"},{"pid":"2afaabc7ecd913227e2bac5471b1cac71af0c15c","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:32:19.000Z","msg":"3/10 曱甴王"},{"pid":"0d722eaf5b4f2d19f4aac55499a19e3f0db74319","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:32:34.000Z","msg":"4/10 曱近平"},{"pid":"5f126ca21438754b74f5f5f062951df09c50c05d","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:32:55.000Z","msg":"5/10 曱甴平"},{"pid":"2c7e8f07d15cc531092d6e449812bfce35e9d17b","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:33:11.000Z","msg":"6/10 曱甴王"},{"pid":"791b632d54592f297388061d1a162981db19ac22","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:33:24.000Z","msg":"7/10 曱近平"},{"pid":"a9cf08946e2e5bc6b9db7347d06ecece47f204a8","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:33:41.000Z","msg":"1/10 曱甴平"},{"pid":"b15dfd5701cb583b149fa09606b2118e9e48e3da","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"8/10 曱甴平"},{"pid":"3bed80acb6057f807d0969e735746e30bc0ef25f","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:34:13.000Z","msg":"9/10 曱甴王"},{"pid":"0b007c1c084ee37a41969d061d2284c8c1b491be","tid":1685934,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"10/10 曱近平"},{"pid":"7908e2fd9d22c517ab2c82065569f03f6d96df77","tid":1685934,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">甴近平</span>"},{"pid":"8932ea2a57fec0109014c8590f29b963123913e0","tid":1685934,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a11ee404d9dbff8579f755373cd24eccf6d9a4a","tid":1685934,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:39:38.000Z","msg":"也所以呢個禁制令一出，<br />\n都冇咩人理。<br />\n<br />\n除非真係濫捕，<br />\n好似上面例子，<br />\n拉哂所有梁國雄。"},{"pid":"79c9c10b51114a6cf2651ce5573255d715a0ce1e","tid":1685934,"uid":217679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:39:46.000Z","msg":"Tui tui <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}